high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the apple off of the counter to the right of the fridge.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the microwave on the counter.
Heat up the apple in the microwave then take it out and close the microwave door.
Walk across the room to the fridge.
Put the heated apple in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick up the tomato to the back of the counter, behind the bread.
Carry the tomato and turn to the right to locate the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the tomato inside. Shut the door then open it and take the tomato out. Shut the door.
Carry the tomato and turn to the left and face the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and place the tomato inside. Shut the door.
Turn to the left and then face the counter to the right, next to the fridge.
Pick the apple up from the counter.
Go right and then turn to the left to face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the apple out again.
Go left and cross the room to turn right and face the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple in the fridge.
